<template>
    <button @click="changeTab()">Tab A</button>
    <button @click="changeTab()">Tab B</button>
    <button @click="changeTab()">Tab C</button>

    <component :is="activeTab"></component>

</template>

<script>
import TabA from "./to_remove/TabA.vue"
import TabB from "./to_remove/TabB.vue"
import TabC from "./to_remove/TabC.vue"

export default {
    name: "AnalytictsBillView",
    components: {
        TabA,
        TabB,
        TabC
    },
    methods: {
        changeTab() {
            this.activeTab = 'Tab A'
        }
    },
    data() {
        return {
            activeTab: "TabA",
        }
    }

}
</script>

</style>
